  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In active phase of thyroid eye disease some patients have obvious upper lid retraction , and
      sometimes exposure keratopathy .To date there is not any standard treatment for this
      situation . We are going to compare the natural course of the upper lid retraction with
      injection of botulinum toxin A injection to upper lid percutaneously.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
